## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on standardized testing. Some sources may have inherent biases based on their organizational goals or perspectives. Additionally, the rapidly evolving educational landscape means that new developments may not be fully captured in this report. Further research and longitudinal studies are recommended to provide a more nuanced understanding of the effectiveness of standardized tests.

